export const homeObjOne = {
    id:'about',
    lightBg:true,
    lightText:false,
    lightTextDesc:false,
    topLine:'Akylbek Muratbek uulu',
    headLine:'About me',
    description:` I'm a student, working toward my degree and looking for ways to put my new knowledge and skills to use in a work environment.`,
    buttonLabel:'Get started',
    imgStart:false,
    img:require('../../images/svg-8.svg'),
    alt:'Car',
    dark:false,
    primary:false,
    darkText:true
};


export const homeObjTwo = {
    id:'discover',
    lightBg:true,
    lightText:false,
    lightTextDesc:false,
    topLine:'Akylbek Muratbek uulu',
    headLine:`Experience`,
    description:`Creative Front-End Developer offering 1 years of experience providing
    high-impact web solutions for diverse industry organizations. Skilled in
    designing, developing and testing multiple web-based applications
    incorporating a range of technologies. Aspiring to combine broad
    background with strong technical skills to excel as a Front-End
    Developer. `,
    buttonLabel:'Learn more',
    imgStart:true,
    img:require('../../images/svg-2.svg'),
    alt:'Piggybank',
    dark:false,
    primary:false,
    darkText:true
